Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.54,0:00:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}创世之初 冥冥之中{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}In the beginning, there was darkness...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.04,0:00:06.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}随着轰的一声{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}and then, bang...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.17,0:00:09.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}诞生了无限膨胀的{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}giving birth to an endless expanding existence...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.38,0:00:11.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}时间 空间和物质{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}of time, space, and matter.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.97,0:00:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}现在 所见超乎我们的想象{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Now, see further than we've ever imagined...{\r}
