Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.19,0:00:26.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}宇宙萌生宇宙{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Universes budding off other universes.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.73,0:00:30.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那里拷贝不走样{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Ewhere there could be an exact copy...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.61,0:00:34.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}同样是我们的太阳系 我们的地球 我们每一个人{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}of our solar system, our Earth, and each one of us.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.57,0:00:36.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那里 一切都大致相同{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Where everything's pretty much the same{\r}
