Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.24,0:00:41.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}然而其它宇宙究竟在哪里呢?{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}But where are these other universes?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.91,0:00:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}为何我们看不到它们呢?{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Why can't we see them?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.04,0:00:45.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}因为我们身处不同的维度里{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Because we're in different dimensions.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.87,0:00:47.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这可是真的吗?{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Can this be true?{\r}
