Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.21,0:00:51.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那么这个实验将会发现它们{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}this experiment will find them.{\r}
