Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.97,0:00:59.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}而在于它们是否存在一 二 三 四种不同的类型{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}but whether there's one, two, three, or four different kinds of them.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.26,0:01:05.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这种耸人听闻意味着宇宙淹没在浩瀚的平行宇宙之中{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}This sensationally means the universe sits in a sea of parallel universes.{\r}
