Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.70,0:01:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}其太阳系和行星完全和我们的一模一样{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}with a solar system and a planet exactly like ours.{\r}
