Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.05,0:01:37.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你可以安享完全相同的人生{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}You could be leading exactly the same life...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.93,0:01:39.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}但是是在另一个宇宙里{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}but in another universe.{\r}
