Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.27,0:01:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你可以过上稍有不同的人生{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}where you could be living a slightly different life...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.44,0:01:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}就在你度过这辈子的同时{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}at the same time as you live this life.{\r}
