Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.32,0:01:57.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}但是外头有可能存在着许多其它的宇宙{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}but there could be many other universes out there.{\r}
