Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.86,0:02:37.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}平行宇宙的概念是我们流行文化的一部分{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}The idea of a parallel universe is part of our popular culture.{\r}
