Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.50,0:02:57.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}似乎表明我们所见到的一切{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}seem to indicate that all that we see...{\r}
