Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.47,0:03:06.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那只是因为我们无法看到某些东西 就以为它不存在{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}thatjust because we can't see something, it ain't there.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.64,0:03:12.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}在我祖母还是小姑娘时 举个例子{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}When my grandma was a little girl, for instance...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.23,0:03:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}他们还不知道还有其它的星系{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}they still didn't know that there were other galaxies.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.28,0:03:19.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}现在我们知道了{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Now we know that there are...{\r}
