Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.64,0:04:34.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}微观尺度上的量子物理学{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Quantum physics at the microscopic scale...{\r}
